{"title":"刮地风（二首）——日本人民和平大游行颂","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮地风（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——日本人民和平大游行颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十方行脚向来无"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此规模："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二千二百万人俱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里征途。?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云旗雷鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾城盈谷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老弱壶浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶携歌哭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海波翻巨吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岳动欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真掀起弥天众怒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮槎八月自遥方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜会扶桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同仇何惮道修长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携手同行。?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长崎谁葬？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲绳谁攘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又窃佳名——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“安全保障”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪炉销铁券，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨掌制强梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且一试人民力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?日本人民和平大游行，全国各地参加者二千二百万人，行程共达一万公里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?八月五日各路游行队伍会师东京，出席禁止原子弹氢弹世界大会各国代表均参加游行。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}